feat(interview): free live video interview — browser STT/TTS + scoring + credit gate

Reworks the live video interview to a 100% free, no-paid-API stack and
wires it into the real interview economy + badge pipeline.

- Fix camera: Permissions-Policy was camera=() (blocked everywhere) →
  camera=(self), so getUserMedia can prompt (next.config.ts)
- Free brain: callGeminiVision (free-tier Gemini, key rotation, optional
  camera frame) + getInterviewerReply action (spoken-style plain text)
- Free voice: browser SpeechSynthesis (slow rate + lower pitch = firm,
  professional) and Web Speech API STT, with a typed-answer fallback
- Credit gate: starting a live interview spends 1 AI Interview credit
  (General fallback w/ confirm) via the existing createInterviewSession
- Scoring: End & grade runs finalizeInterview → same rubric, pass gate,
  and Verified Skill badge issuance as text interviews; result panel
- Light vision: one camera frame sent per turn for engagement awareness
- Remove dead paid Gemini-Live token route (kept config for future)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
